---
title: Golden Thai-Style Chicken Curry with Chow Mein
description: Pure comfort in Thai curry form! Based off of the famed Thai 'Khao Soi' curry, this warming dish is sure to be a hit. With a delicious coconut-based broth covering unctuous chow mein noodles, every bite will be better than the last!
